<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 02:56:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普级战列舰将采用核动力</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/trump-class-battleships-will-be-nuclear-powered</link><description>&lt;p&gt;为特朗普级配备核推进装置带来了好处，但也带来了巨大的挑战，海军官员一直反对这一想法。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/trump-class-battleships-will-be-nuclear-powered"&gt;后特朗普级战列舰将采用核动力&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 May 2026 00:38:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/trump-class-battleships-will-be-nuclear-powered</guid></item><item><title>随着谈判陷入僵局，回收伊朗浓缩铀的可能性似乎有所上升（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/possibility-of-operation-to-retrieve-irans-enriched-uranium-appears-to-rise-as-negotiations-sputter</link><description>&lt;p&gt;特朗普和内塔尼亚胡在过去 24 小时内都发表评论，指出可能存在夺取伊朗核材料的高风险行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/possibility-of-operation-to-retrieve-irans-enriched-uranium-appears-to-rise-as-negotiations-sputter"&gt;随着谈判的进展，回收伊朗浓缩铀行动的可能性似乎上升（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 23:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/possibility-of-operation-to-retrieve-irans-enriched-uranium-appears-to-rise-as-negotiations-sputter</guid></item><item><title>MQ-9“死神”在测试中发射激光制导火箭</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-slings-drone-killing-laser-guided-rockets-in-tests</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着对低成本反无人机武器的需求激增，MQ-9 成功测试了针对空中和地面目标的 APKWS 火箭。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-slings-drone-killing-laser-guided-rockets-in-tests"&gt;MQ-9“死神”后发射激光制导火箭的测试&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 21:59:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mq-9-reaper-slings-drone-killing-laser-guided-rockets-in-tests</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯巡逻艇出现反无人机“顶笼”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/anti-drone-cope-cage-appears-on-russian-patrol-boat</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰无人机对海军目标的攻击正在推动新防御系统的发展，但仅头顶屏幕的功效正在下降。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/anti-drone-cope-cage-appears-on-russian-patrol-boat"&gt;俄罗斯巡逻艇出现反无人机“顶笼”&lt;/a&gt;后，首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 18:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/anti-drone-cope-cage-appears-on-russian-patrol-boat</guid></item><item><title>C-5 星系预计将继续飞行到 2050 年，准备度骤降至 37%</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/c-5-galaxies-now-slated-to-keep-flying-until-2050-as-readiness-plummets-to-37-percent</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军的库存中没有任何一款飞机可以做到 C-5 的功能，但即使在进行了昂贵的升级之后，它们仍然非常脾气暴躁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;随着&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;准备&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/c-5-galaxies-now-slated-to-keep-flying-until-2050-as-readiness-plummets-to-37-percent"&gt;度骤降至 37%，后 C-5 星系预计将继续飞行到 2050 年&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 16:53:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/c-5-galaxies-now-slated-to-keep-flying-until-2050-as-readiness-plummets-to-37-percent</guid></item><item><title>截至2026年5月11日，航母在哪里：20艘军舰执行伊朗封锁</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-carriers-as-of-may-11-2026-20-warships-including-two-carriers-enforce-iran-blockade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;与此同时，尼米兹号航空母舰在环绕南美航行并重新定位前往诺福克的巡航过程中在里约停靠。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;截至 2026 年 5 月 11 日，&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;航母&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-carriers-as-of-may-11-2026-20-warships-including-two-carriers-enforce-iran-blockade"&gt;在哪里：20 艘军舰执行伊朗封锁&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 04:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/where-are-the-carriers-as-of-may-11-2026-20-warships-including-two-carriers-enforce-iran-blockade</guid></item><item><title>DARPA 寻求将无人机群装入不起眼的集装箱中</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-swarms-packed-into-unassuming-containers-sought-by-darpa</link><description>&lt;p&gt;远程触发的集装箱式无人机群可能被放置在敌方后方，对几乎任何地方的威胁造成难以防御的威胁。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-swarms-packed-into-unassuming-containers-sought-by-darpa"&gt;DARPA 寻求的无人机群装进不起眼的集装箱的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 18:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/drone-swarms-packed-into-unassuming-containers-sought-by-darpa</guid></item><item><title>F/A-18 超级大黄蜂向封锁中的伊朗油轮的烟囱投下炸弹（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-a-18-super-hornet-drops-bombs-down-smoke-stacks-of-iranian-tankers-running-blockade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;此次袭击发生之际，阿联酋声称再次遭到伊朗袭击，而就在美国和伊朗交火数小时后。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-a-18-super-hornet-drops-bombs-down-smoke-stacks-of-iranian-tankers-running-blockade"&gt;F/A-18 超级大黄蜂向封锁中的伊朗油轮的烟囱投下炸弹（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/f-a-18-super-hornet-drops-bombs-down-smoke-stacks-of-iranian-tankers-running-blockade</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-191</link><description>&lt;p&gt;混凝土是新的黑色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-191"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:37:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-191</guid></item><item><title>土耳其追求洲际弹道导弹的背后是什么？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/nuclear/what-is-behind-turkeys-pursuit-of-an-icbm</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一枚此前未知的洲际弹道导弹的意外曝光引发了人们对安卡拉战略野心的重大质疑。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/nuclear/what-is-behind-turkeys-pursuit-of-an-icbm"&gt;土耳其追求洲际弹道导弹的背后是什么？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 18:27:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/nuclear/what-is-behind-turkeys-pursuit-of-an-icbm</guid></item></channel></rss>